These are Puzzles for 3x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-1::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: folk, soul, dubstep
There are 3 different nationalities: mexican, american, nigerian
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: water-polo, handball, biathlon
1. the person who's sport is biathlon is in an even position##4
2. the american is on the left of the mexican##1
3. the fan of folk is on the right of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
4. the american is in an even position##4
5. the fan of dubstep is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |    3     |
| Music-Genre   | dubstep       | folk     | soul    |
| Nationality   | nigerian   | american          | mexican   |
| Sport         | water-polo | biathlon | handball |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-2::.
There 3 different types of food: orange, cherry, peas
The people have 3 different hobbies: fishing, writing, baking
The people have 3 different jobs:  security-guard, engineer, firefighter
1. the firefighter is the person eating peas##1
2. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left or right of the firefighter##3
3. the person eating peas is on the left of the person eating cherry##1
4. the engineer is on the right of the person who's hobby is writing##1
5. the firefighter is in an even position##4
6. the firefighter is on the right of the person who's hobby is baking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2      |    3     |
| Food    | orange     | peas  | cherry  |
| Hobby   | baking | writing | fishing    |
| Job     | security-guard      | firefighter    | engineer |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-3::.
There 3 different types of food: grapes, cauliflower, garlic
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: disco, indie, salsa
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: tennis, cricket, handball
1. the person who's sport is tennis is in an even position##4
2. the person who's sport is handball is the person eating grapes##1
3. the fan of salsa is on the right of the fan of disco##1
4. the person eating garlic is on the right of the person eating grapes##1
5. the person eating garlic is on the left or right of the fan of salsa##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |   3    |
| Food          | grapes         | garlic     | cauliflower   |
| Music-Genre   | indie       | disco     | salsa |
| Sport         | handball | tennis | cricket |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-4::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, tea, milk
The people have 3 different jobs:  lawyer, chef, musician
3 different pets are kept: lizard, hedgehog, dog
1. the person drinking milk is on the left of the owner of the dog##1
2. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the musician##1
3. the lawyer is in an odd position##4
4. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far left##1
5. the musician is on the far left or far right##3
6. the chef is on the right of the musician##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2     |       3       |
| Beverage   | iced-tea | milk  | tea |
| Job        | musician | chef  | lawyer |
| Pet        | lizard | hedgehog | dog         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-5::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: disaster, action, fantasy
There are 3 different nationalities: thai, brazilian, canadian
3 different pets are kept: frog, hedgehog, horse
1. the thai is on the left or right of the owner of the frog##3
2. the brazilian is on the left of the owner of the horse##1
3. the owner of the frog is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1
4. the owner of the frog is in an odd position##4
5. the person watching fantasy movies is on the far left##1
6. the person watching action movies is on the left or right of the person watching disaster movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |    3    |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy | disaster  | action  |
| Nationality   | brazilian  | thai | canadian |
| Pet           | hedgehog  | horse    | frog    |

