.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-6::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: coffee, water, 7up
The people have 3 different hobbies: baking, woodworking, gardening
The people use 3 different means of transport: helicopter, snowmobile, skateboard
1. the person drinking coffee is between the person driving the skateboard and the person who's hobby is gardening##2
2. the person who's hobby is baking is the person drinking water##1
3. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1
4. the person driving the snowmobile is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |   2   |      3      |
| Beverage    | 7up  | coffee  | water        |
| Hobby       | gardening | woodworking | baking |
| Transport   | helicopter    | snowmobile   | skateboard   |

