3. the person who's sport is cycling is in an even position##4
4. the person watching documentary movies is on the right of the person who's sport is water-polo##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |       2       |    3    |
| Movie-Genre   | drama | documentary        | romance |
| Pet           | dog   | bird      | lizard     |
| Sport         | water-polo | cycling | biathlon    |

