.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-8::.
There 3 different types of food: nectarine, raspberry, avocado
The people have 3 different jobs:  dressmaker, videographer, lawyer
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: ice-hockey, rowing, weightlifting
1. the person eating raspberry is on the right of the person eating nectarine##1
2. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is between the lawyer and the person eating avocado##2
3. the videographer is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
4. the person eating avocado is in an odd position##4
5. the person who's sport is weightlifting is the person eating avocado##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2     |      3       |
| Food    | nectarine   | raspberry | avocado       |
| Job     | lawyer  | dressmaker  | videographer |
| Sport   | rowing | ice-hockey  | weightlifting       |

