.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-9::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: cooking, drawing, fishing
There are 3 different nationalities: japanese, australian, spanish
3 different pets are kept: dog, pony, hedgehog
1. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
2. the japanese is in an odd position##4
3. the australian is on the left or right of the owner of the pony##3
4. the japanese is on the right of the australian##1
5. the person who's hobby is cooking is between the owner of the dog and the person who's hobby is drawing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |       3       |
| Hobby         | drawing | cooking | fishing |
| Nationality   | spanish       | australian  | japanese     |
| Pet           | pony     | hedgehog     | dog          |

