.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-10::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  project-manager, fisherman, librarian
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: fantasy, western, family
There are 3 different nationalities: dutch, pakistani, malaysian
1. the fisherman is on the far right##1
2. the person watching western movies is the person watching western movies##1
3. the dutch is on the left or right of the malaysian##3
4. the project-manager is on the right of the person watching western movies##1
5. the malaysian is on the left of the person watching family movies##1
6. the person watching family movies is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |    3    |
| Job           | librarian | project-manager        | fisherman   |
| Movie-Genre   | western | family | fantasy    |
| Nationality   | malaysian         | dutch      | pakistani |

