1. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left of the person watching musical movies##1
2. the fan of metal is the owner of the hamster##1
3. the owner of the hamster is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
4. the person watching time-travel movies is the fan of d&b##1
5. the person watching musical movies is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |   3    |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel      | musical | documentary |
| Music-Genre   | d&b        | metal         | disco |
| Pet           | rat | hamster         | goat   |

