1. the person drinking milk is on the left of the owner of the bird##1
2. the person driving the boat is on the left or right of the person driving the motorbike##3
3. the owner of the bird is in an odd position##4
4. the owner of the pony is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
5. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person drinking water##1
6. the owner of the pony is on the left or right of the person driving the boat##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2     |     3      |
| Beverage    | cola | milk      | water     |
| Pet         | dog  | pony | bird        |
| Transport   | bus | motorbike    | boat |

