.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-20::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: skydiving, board-games, video-games
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: family, superhero, disaster
3 different pets are kept: pony, goldfish, goat
1. the person who's hobby is board-games is between the person who's hobby is skydiving and the person watching superhero movies##2
2. the owner of the goat is in an odd position##4
3. the owner of the goat is in an odd position##4
4. the person watching disaster movies is the owner of the goldfish##1
5. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the owner of the pony##1
6. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is video-games##3
7. the person watching family movies is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |     3      |
| Hobby         | video-games      | board-games | skydiving |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero | family      | disaster    |
| Pet           | goat      | pony        | goldfish       |

 